en_989681_0	The Police Headquarters Official’ say that a special traffic plan had been implemented around the Bandaranaike International Airport from Tuesday, January 3, owing to the upgrades to be carried out on its runway.
en_989681_1	As a result, the new traffic plan will be in effect till April 6 from 3 p.m. to 9 a.m.
en_989681_2	The renovation of the runway of the BIA is to be commenced on January 6.
en_989681_3	As part of the new traffic plan, a number of alternate routes have been introduced to vehicles arriving on the Colombo – Katunayake expressway, and from Colombo, Chilaw and Minuwangoda.
en_989681_4	In addition, police said that a special traffic plan has been introduced to facilitate vehicles entering and exiting the Katunayake Investment Promotion Zone.
